Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？琳達學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
